<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pizzeria RealPizza</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/Site.css" />
    <style>

        body {
            background-color: #f7f4e9;
            ;
        }
        
        header {
            background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1619853618139-fe43aff572fa?q=80&w=3431&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D'); 
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        
        main {
            padding: 50px;
        }

        section.container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            footer a {
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

                
    </style>
</head>


<body>
    <header class="container-fluid rounded-4">
        <h1 class="text-white">Pizzeria RealPizza</h1>
        <p class="text-white">L'arte della pizza incontra la passione culinaria autentica.</p>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Il Nostro Menu</h2>
                    <p>Esplora una vasta selezione di pizze artigianali, realizzate con ingredienti freschi e genuini.</p>
                    @Html.ActionLink("Menu", "Index", "Pizze", null, new {@class = "BtnAcq"})
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="~/Content/Immagini/MenuSection.jpg" alt="Menu" class="img-fluid rounded-3 w-100 h-100">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="~/Content/Immagini/DeliverySection.jpg" alt="Consegne a domicilio" class="img-fluid rounded-3 w-100 h-100">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Consegne a domicilio</h2>
                    <p>Gusta le nostre pizze direttamente a casa tua, grazie al nostro servizio di consegna rapida.</p>
                    <p>Ordina online o chiamaci al numero 0932456984</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Vieni a trovarci</h2>
                    <p>Vi aspettiamo nel nostro accogliente ristorante. Assaporate l'autentica esperienza della pizza con noi.</p>
                    <p>Indirizzo: Via Roma, 123 - Città</p>
                    <p>Orari: Martedì-Domenica 12:00-23:00</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <iframe class="rounded-3" width="400" height="250" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d6844565.288961146!2d84.72806645772494!3d33.10716738328714!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x376530c9d373a977%3A0x83b13173a523ec44!2sPrefettura%20di%20Nagqu%2C%20Tibet%2C%20Cina!5e0!3m2!1sit!2sit!4v1710356405606!5m2!1sit!2sit"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
